Provides classes for modeling Lighter applications at compile-time

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Controller
    Represents a ResourceController annotated class.
    Endpoint
    HTTP endpoint that in the application.
    MethodParameter
    A single parameter on an Endpoint handler method.
    Model
    The top level class which represents the application.
    ParameterParser
    Parser for path and query parameters.
    QueryParams
    Endpoint HTTP query parameters.
    RequestGuardFactory
    Represents a RequestGuardFactory implementation in the application.
    RequestGuards
    Top level Request Guard model class which represents the mapping between RequestGuards and RequestGuardFactorys.
    Route
    Represents a route constructed from a template String.
    RoutePart
    A single component of a Route.
